gem "honeybadger", "~> 4.0"
bundle install
bundle exec honeybadger install 30a79402

Source
https://dev.to/sylvance/monitoring-using-honeybadger-and-rails-activesupport-instrumentation-3074
https://docs.honeybadger.io/

In order to notify in honeybadger for dev and test mode, setup in honeybadger.yml file.
development:
  report_data: true